es.esi.techlab.bluebeetooth

Class BluetoothIO

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.bluetooth.BluetoothGattCallback
      • es.esi.techlab.bluebeetooth.BluetoothIO

  • public final class BluetoothIO
extends android.bluetooth.BluetoothGattCallback
    BluetoothIO is the main class in order to make and receive the bluetooth communications from the smartphone to the bluetooth device. This class extends from the default BluetoothGattCallback class.
    See Also:
    BluetoothGattCallback, BluetoothGatt
